üìÑ Documentation: Flask Local File Dashboard
Overview
The Flask Local File Dashboard is a web application that scans a folder on your computer, categorizes files by type (images, documents, spreadsheets, audio, videos, others), and displays the distribution using a pie chart powered by Chart.js. This project demonstrates how Flask can be used to interact with the local file system and present data visually in a browser.

Features
Scans a specified folder on your laptop.

Categorizes files into predefined types.

Counts the number of files in each category.

Displays results in a responsive pie chart.

Provides a quick overview of your local file distribution.

Project Structure
Code
FlaskFileDashboard/
